title: Hawaiian Homecoming
description: Hawaiian Homecoming by Bill And Gloria Gaither is an inspirational collection of great gospel tunes by this exceptiional contemporary Christian songwriting duo who have been one of this genre's most successful artists. Songs on this uplifting album include 'Palms Of Victory,' 'Born Again,' 'Hear My Song, Lord,' and 'Mary, Did You Know'' to name just a few. Don't miss out on this excitiing set of religious gems that is sure to make a wonderful addition to your music library. TRACK LISTING 01. Palms Of Victory 02. Songs That Answer Questions 03. Go Tell 04. When He Blessed My Soul 05. 'Til The Storm Passes By 06. At The Cross 07. Born Again 08. God Will Make A Way 09. Promises One By One 10. I Don't Think, I Know 11. Jesus, I Believe What You Said 12. I Wish You 13. Hear My Song, Lord 14. I'm Free 15. Mary Was The First One To Carry The Gospel 16. Mary, Did You Know' 17. King Is Coming
